{"tid":1026504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"現實版Iron Man　英軍基地亮相噴射飛行器","createTime":"2019-02-18T07:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T04:24:59.000Z","uid":184679,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"1e9bdcb09f0a88de681cca760441db6395fd8652","tid":1026504,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T07:26:17.000Z","msg":"科幻電影中「鐵甲奇俠」飛上半空的畫面有望在現實出現？英國皇家海軍近日在訓練基地，展示噴射飛行器，飛上半空越過障礙賽道，軍方更不排除將來或將技術應用在軍事用途。<br />\n<br />\n外國科技網站The Verge報道指，噴射飛行器公司Gravity Industries上周在英國皇家突擊隊的訓練基地，展示噴射飛行器Daedalus Mark 1，該飛行器配備6組小型噴射引擎，2個位於背部，另外4個分別安裝在左右兩臂，使用者戴上飛行器後就可在空中自由移動。<br />\n<br />\n曾是英國皇家海軍一員，如今已是噴射飛行器公司老闆的Richard Browning更親身上陣，示範如何透過噴射飛行器穿越障礙物。根據英國皇家海軍的說法，今次示範並不代表已開始計劃為英國士兵引入個人噴射飛行器，但飛行器具備速度和自由移動等功能，不難看出未來或有可能應用在軍事用途上。<br />\n<br />\n不過，目前Daedalus Mark 1仍要解決噪音、飛行時間等問題，方可真正應用在現實當中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aFQSFke0wFc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaFQSFke0wFc&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=9521c812\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aFQSFke0wFc</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2257334/%E7%8F%BE%E5%AF%A6%E7%89%88Iron%20Man%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%80%E8%8B%B1%E8%BB%8D%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%AE%E7%9B%B8%E5%99%B4%E5%B0%84%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%99%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2257334%2F%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%2589%2588Iron%2520Man%25EF%25BC%259F%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%259F%25BA%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%25AE%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%2599%25B4%25E5%25B0%2584%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%2599%25A8&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgN%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=08bcc551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2257334/%E7%8F%BE%E5%AF%A6%E7%89%88Iron%20Man%EF%BC%9F%E3%80%80%E8%8B%B1%E8%BB%8D%E5%9F%BA%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%AE%E7%9B%B8%E5%99%B4%E5%B0%84%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%99%A8</a>"},{